    "Researchers can develop techniques to incorporate human feedback into the training process of DL models.",
    "This can help to improve the interpretability of the models and make them more useful for clinical decision-making.",
    "Researchers can work on developing standards for interpretability in DL models.",
    "This can help ensure that models are transparent and that clinicians understand how they arrived at their decisions.",
    "Researchers can evaluate the impact of interpretability on the adoption of DL models in clinical settings."
